\f1\b0\fs38 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}4 large egg whites at room temperature\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 teaspoon {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/cream-of-tartar/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 cream of tartar}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 cup plus 2 tablespoons superfine granulated sugar\
